articles.title: About me
articles.description: Some additional details about the blog
articles.contents: I am a behavioral scientist working at Babylon Health on experimentation and tracking. Previously, I was a PhD student at Warwick Business School where I did research on judgement and decision making, specifically how people make decisions over time and from experience. I use this blog to write about behavioral science, data science, and design.
